Package: shinyoats
Type: Package
Title: Oat UI Components for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali",
           email = "prm@outlook.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7864-5819")),
    person("Kailash", "Nadh",
           role = "cph",
           comment = "Oat UI library author")
    )
Description: Provides Shiny bindings for the Oat UI component library
    (<https://github.com/knadh/oat>), a lightweight, zero-dependency,
    semantic HTML/CSS/JS UI framework. Enables building modern Shiny applications
    with Oat's clean design system including buttons, cards, forms, grids, tabs,
    modals, toasts, and more. Offers 55 ready-to-use components as clean R
    wrapper functions requiring no knowledge of CSS classes or HTML.
